```text
Act as a senior Alpine Linux, iSH, POSIX shell, TUI, and systems installer architect.

Your job is to turn my iSH TUI draft into a full-featured, production-quality TUI installer for iSH on Alpine Linux x86.

Prioritize correctness, maintainability, idempotency, safe config writes, iSH compatibility, and real-world launch readiness.
