## 14. Launch-readiness checklist

The agent must not call it launch-ready until:

```text
- All shell scripts pass sh syntax check
- TUI runs in iSH
- apk operations are guarded
- no x86_64-only packages are used
- no systemd assumptions exist
- no duplicate aliases are generated
- rerunning installer does not duplicate config blocks
- backup files are created before config writes
- failed modules can be retried
- logs are written
- final report is generated
- README has install/run instructions
- TESTING.md documents iSH manual testing
```

